    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 97629.0,
      "end_time": 98462.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] So after watching that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 98462.0,
      "end_time": 99720.0,
      "text": "I think we can all agree"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 99720.0,
      "end_time": 102770.0,
      "text": "that meditating is at least a little bit helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 102770.0,
      "end_time": 104979.0,
      "text": "But what exactly does it do for us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 104980.0,
      "end_time": 107930.0,
      "text": "Because there are so many benefits to meditation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 107930.0,
      "end_time": 109870.0,
      "text": "I don't have time to go through all of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 109870.0,
      "end_time": 112100.0,
      "text": "but I am going to go over my top five"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 112100.0,
      "end_time": 114890.0,
      "text": "personal favorite reasons to meditate."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 114890.0,
      "end_time": 117850.0,
      "text": "The first main point is that meditation improves"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 117850.0,
      "end_time": 120640.0,
      "text": "learning, memory and self-awareness."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 120640.0,
      "end_time": 123870.0,
      "text": "Long term practice of meditation increases"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 123870.0,
      "end_time": 126780.0,
      "text": "grey matter density in the areas of the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 126780.0,
      "end_time": 128960.0,
      "text": "associated with self-awareness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 128960.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131470.0,
      "text": "compassion and introspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 131470.0,
      "end_time": 134200.0,
      "text": "Grey matter is made up of the cell bodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134200.0,
      "end_time": 135670.0,
      "text": "of nerve cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 135670.0,
      "end_time": 138350.0,
      "text": "So basically, the more grey matter you have"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 138350.0,
      "end_time": 140299.0,
      "text": "in a certain area of your brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 140300.0,
      "end_time": 143550.0,
      "text": "the smarter you'll become in that certain area."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 143550.0,
      "end_time": 145690.0,
      "text": "And in my opinion, self-awareness"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 145690.0,
      "end_time": 147829.0,
      "text": "is the number one most important trait"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 147830.0,
      "end_time": 150380.0,
      "text": "when it comes to being successful in business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 150380.0,
      "end_time": 153690.0,
      "text": "relationships, school, or really anything at all in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 153690.0,
      "end_time": 156570.0,
      "text": "The second reason is that mindfulness meditation"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 156570.0,
      "end_time": 158910.0,
      "text": "decreases feelings of loneliness."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 158910.0,
      "end_time": 161107.0,
      "text": "A study from the Carnegie Mellon University"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161107.0,
      "end_time": 164320.0,
      "text": "indicates that mindfulness meditation training"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 164320.0,
      "end_time": 167459.0,
      "text": "is useful in decreasing feelings of loneliness"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167460.0,
      "end_time": 169720.0,
      "text": "which in turn decreases the risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169720.0,
      "end_time": 171840.0,
      "text": "of morbidity and mortality."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171840.0,
      "end_time": 174320.0,
      "text": "As I've said in the past, I believe a big reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174320.0,
      "end_time": 177140.0,
      "text": "why people don't get into the right relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 177140.0,
      "end_time": 179857.0,
      "text": "is because they're often looking for another person"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179857.0,
      "end_time": 181609.0,
      "text": "to complete them."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 181610.0,
      "end_time": 184460.0,
      "text": "But when you practice meditating and you decrease"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 184460.0,
      "end_time": 186870.0,
      "text": "that feeling of loneliness and you decrease"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 186870.0,
      "end_time": 188450.0,
      "text": "that incomplete feeling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 188450.0,
      "end_time": 190600.0,
      "text": "you're much more likely to find the right person"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 190600.0,
      "end_time": 192380.0,
      "text": "who will make you truly happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 192380.0,
      "end_time": 195299.0,
      "text": "The third benefit of meditation is that it lengthens"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 195300.0,
      "end_time": 197940.0,
      "text": "your attention span, and I think today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 197940.0,
      "end_time": 200400.0,
      "text": "with all the distractions in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 200400.0,
      "end_time": 202100.0,
      "text": "this is more important than ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 202100.0,
      "end_time": 204489.0,
      "text": "To put it simply, if you do something called"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 204490.0,
      "end_time": 206460.0,
      "text": "focused-attention meditation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206460.0,
      "end_time": 209120.0,
      "text": "you're basically training your attention span,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 209120.0,
      "end_time": 212348.0,
      "text": "similar to how you would train your biceps in the gym."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 212348.0,
      "end_time": 214820.0,
      "text": "If you do this on a regular basis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 214820.0,
      "end_time": 217530.0,
      "text": "you will be able to focus on a certain task"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 217530.0,
      "end_time": 220680.0,
      "text": "for much longer without getting distracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 220680.0,
      "end_time": 222700.0,
      "text": "It does not have to be a lot of meditating."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 222700.0,
      "end_time": 225489.0,
      "text": "In fact, a study has shown that if you practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 225490.0,
      "end_time": 227980.0,
      "text": "meditation for only four days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 227980.0,
      "end_time": 229560.0,
      "text": "this actually could be enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 229560.0,
      "end_time": 231670.0,
      "text": "to increase your attention span."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 231670.0,
      "end_time": 235910.0,
      "text": "The fourth reason is that meditation helps fight addictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 235910.0,
      "end_time": 237720.0,
      "text": "Now when I say the word addictions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 237720.0,
      "end_time": 240800.0,
      "text": "I don't necessarily mean big addictions"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 240800.0,
      "end_time": 242280.0,
      "text": "like being addicted to drugs or alcohol"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 242280.0,
      "end_time": 244940.0,
      "text": "but I'm also talking about small addictions"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 244940.0,
      "end_time": 246980.0,
      "text": "like constantly checking your Instagram,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 246980.0,
      "end_time": 248799.0,
      "text": "constantly checking your Facebook messages"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 248800.0,
      "end_time": 250800.0,
      "text": "or even your emails"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 250800.0,
      "end_time": 253830.0,
      "text": "or simply just being addicted to your phone in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 253830.0,
      "end_time": 257160.0,
      "text": "The mental discipline you can develop through meditation"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 257160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258921.00000000003,
      "text": "may help you break dependencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 258921.0,
      "end_time": 262280.0,
      "text": "by increasing your self-control and awareness"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 262280.0,
      "end_time": 265320.0,
      "text": "of the triggers for addictive behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 265320.0,
      "end_time": 268530.0,
      "text": "One study that taught 19 recovering alcoholics"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 268530.0,
      "end_time": 271200.0,
      "text": "how to meditate, found that participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 271200.0,
      "end_time": 272940.0,
      "text": "who received the training"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 272940.0,
      "end_time": 275140.0,
      "text": "got much better at controlling their cravings"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 275140.0,
      "end_time": 279159.0,
      "text": "and it lowered the stress associated with the cravings."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 279160.0,
      "end_time": 281340.0,
      "text": "And again, this is linked to building"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 281340.0,
      "end_time": 284119.0,
      "text": "that grey matter density in the self-awareness"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 284120.0,
      "end_time": 285380.0,
      "text": "part of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 285380.0,
      "end_time": 287770.0,
      "text": "The fifth main benefit of meditation"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 287770.0,
      "end_time": 290990.0,
      "text": "is that it reduces stress and anxiety in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 290990.0,
      "end_time": 293600.0,
      "text": "A study from the University of Wisconsin-Madison"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 293600.0,
      "end_time": 298800.0,
      "text": "indicates that the practice of open monitoring meditation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 298800.0,
      "end_time": 301303.0,
      "text": "which again, is just a very basic form of meditation"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 301303.0,
      "end_time": 303860.0,
      "text": "reduces the grey matter density"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 303860.0,
      "end_time": 308100.0,
      "text": "in the areas of the brain related with anxiety and stress."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 308100.0,
      "end_time": 310680.0,
      "text": "Meditators were much more able to attend"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 310680.0,
      "end_time": 312820.0,
      "text": "moment to moment focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 312820.0,
      "end_time": 315540.0,
      "text": "So all that means is if there was a problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 315540.0,
      "end_time": 317550.0,
      "text": "that entered the meditator's life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 317550.0,
      "end_time": 319810.0,
      "text": "it is much easier for them to move on"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 319810.0,
      "end_time": 322320.0,
      "text": "to the next thing and it's much easier for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 322320.0,
      "end_time": 323730.0,
      "text": "to address the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 323730.0,
      "end_time": 326110.0,
      "text": "While someone who doesn't practice meditation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 326110.0,
      "end_time": 328400.0,
      "text": "oftentimes, they get so hung up"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 328400.0,
      "end_time": 330349.0,
      "text": "on that one problem or issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 330350.0,
      "end_time": 331940.0,
      "text": "it could ruin their whole day"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 331940.0,
      "end_time": 334510.0,
      "text": "and even ruin their week sometimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 334510.0,
      "end_time": 338107.0,
      "text": "I can honestly say that meditation has changed my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 338107.0,
      "end_time": 340210.0,
      "text": "and I'm not trying to sell you anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 340210.0,
      "end_time": 342640.0,
      "text": "I'm not trying to get you to download some app."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 342640.0,
      "end_time": 345890.0,
      "text": "I am just sharing with you how much of a positive impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
